text: Thuận Thiên (Heaven's will) may refer to: * Era name of Lý Thái Tổ from 1010 to 1028 * Empress Consort Thuận Thiên of Trần Thái Tông * The mythical sword Thuận Thiên of Lê Thái Tổ * Era name of Lê Thái Tổ from 1428 to 1433 * Imperial Consort Thuận Thiên of Gia Long ==See also== * Shuntian (disambiguation) (, era names and placenames of China) *Suncheon (, a city in South Korea)
title: Thuan Thien
